Package cz.cvut.fel.omo.hamrazec.services

Class FactoryTimer

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.omo.hamrazec.services.FactoryTimer
public class FactoryTimer
extends java.lang.Object
FactoryTimer is used for simulation of real time. Time is represented by tact that should represent one hour. It is possible to change time of tack for better simulation by calling method timeLapse with argument.
